{"tid":570793,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"以前 EEE 真係難讀到仆街，難到翻炒 PP 都唔識做","createTime":"2018-02-24T04:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T07:20:20.000Z","uid":14170,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ff2f66da820bb9b5c16ea72e00126abc1cf78b2","tid":570793,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"90 年代 HKU EEE 考試真係由頭到尾都係 proof 野，啲 case 天馬行空勁難，啲數學概念深到要用好多數學既 skill 黎 solve。<br />\n<br />\n依家考試已經淺左好多，幾乎有一半題目係 PP 度翻炒，然後 proof 既題目都係 note 度改少少野，有睇過 note 轉少少灣已經做到七八成 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最慘係份卷咁淺我都唔識做，識少少 (做到6成) 已經 A 到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇得出 prof 出卷已經好就住我地，究竟完全版 EEE 有幾癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"281a8fd2394b39b1ed0aee3b4cc367477ea65348","tid":570793,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T04:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c6ffc3197b0ff02d6b634a144c4d684a96e075","tid":570793,"uid":7110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"90年代嘅polyu EE卷都係代式做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990fad30adc5e76e232e3f4adb2af0d160b8445c","tid":570793,"uid":7110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T06:12:06.000Z","msg":"有無天馬行空嘅例子睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a63f63e494c8bacbe7d1e25c4291fdd9f2cd7f","tid":570793,"uid":34884,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5c6ffc3197b0ff02d6b634a144c4d684a96e075","tid":570793,"uid":7110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"90年代嘅polyu EE卷都係代式做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-24T06:15:38.000Z","msg":"唔拉curve代式做好正常<br />\n肯溫書就唔會差得去邊<br />\n<br 